# HNGi7 team-sentry API

Welcome to HNGi7 team-sentry API. A dockerized micro-service for managing static, external pages.

Polls is a simple API allowing consumers to view polls and vote in them.

## List of pages [GET /list_pages]

Here you retrieve all pages stored in DB
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

       + Body
   
                           [
                                        {
                                                    "created": "2020-06-10T20:31:47.685Z",
                                                    "_id": "5ee14f4138871d0024483881",
                                                    "title": "test from postman",
                                                    "content": "content from post man",
                                                    "__v": 0
                                        }
                            ]

## Retrieve A Webpage's HTML [GET /retrieve_page_html]

The requests to this endpoint can be external for external pages and internal for pages stored in the DB

+ Response 200 (application/json)

       + Body
       
                            [
                                        {
                                                    "status": "success",
                                                    "data": "page html"
                                        }
                            
                            ]









